sourcesContent: import React, { Fragment } from 'react' import Title from './Title' import Home from './Home' import FormBlog from './FormBlog' import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, NavLink } from "react-router-dom"; const Header = () => { return ( <div className="btn-group my-3"> <NavLink to="/" exact className="btn btn-light" activeClassName="active">Home</NavLink> <NavLink to="/save-blog" className="btn btn-light" activeClassName="active">Agregar Blog</NavLink> </div> <Switch> <Route path="/save-blog" component={FormBlog} /> <Route path="/" component={Home} /> </Switch> </Fragment> ) } export default Body
